  "title": "management",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>Corporate Secretarial Support</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare\n     and file statutory documents with ACRA, including annual returns, officer\n     changes, share allotments, and resolutions.</li><li>Maintain\n     statutory registers and ensure compliance with the Companies Act.</li><li>Draft\n     board resolutions, minutes, notices, and routine corporate documents.</li><li>Coordinate\n     AGM/EGM documentation and compliance timelines.</li><li>Assist\n     with incorporation, striking off, share transfers, and restructuring\n     matters.</li></ul><p><strong>Accounting & Financial Administration Support</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate\n     monthly closing activities and assist in bookkeeping review.</li><li>Prepare\n     management schedules and supporting documents for accountants.</li><li>Liaise\n     with clients to obtain outstanding documents and clarify accounting\n     queries.</li><li>Support\n     GST, payroll, and CPF data collation.</li><li>Track\n     deadlines for GST filing, tax submissions, and financial statement\n     preparation.</li></ul><p><strong>Compliance & Regulatory Coordination</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain\n     compliance checklists, SOPs, and audit trails.</li><li>Support\n     KYC/AML onboarding and client due diligence.</li><li>Assist\n     in preparing documentation for internal/external audits.</li></ul><p><strong>Client & Stakeholder Coordination</strong></p><ul><li>Serve\n     as the primary coordination point between clients and internal teams.</li><li>Manage\n     client onboarding, service agreements, and annual renewals.</li><li>Handle\n     routine enquiries and escalate technical matters to managers.</li><li>Prepare\n     proposals, quotations, and service scope summaries.</li></ul><p><strong>Operational & Administrative Support</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain\n     digital filing systems and document control.</li><li>Prepare\n     weekly/monthly operational reports for management.</li><li>Support\n     workflow planning, resource scheduling, and process improvements.</li></ul>",
